# Files and directories to ignore when building AI context
# These patterns reduce noise and prevent leaking sensitive or irrelevant data to agentic tools.

# Lock files and package manager caches
**/package-lock.json
**/yarn.lock
**/pnpm-lock.yaml
**/.npm

# Build outputs and caches
**/dist
**/build
**/.next
**/.cache
**/.turbo
**/node_modules
**/storybook-static
**/coverage

# Generated token and component artefacts
packages/tokens/dist
packages/components/dist

# Archives and tarballs
**/*.tgz
**/*.zip

# Environment files
**/.env
**/.env.*

# Legacy or archived code
**/v1-archive
**/legacy

# Binary assets (images, PDFs, docs) that are not used in code
**/*.png
**/*.jpg
**/*.jpeg
**/*.gif
**/*.svg
**/*.pdf

# Exclude storybook build artefacts
storybook-static
